{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2282289, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "胃镜，管子不粗，喝上麻药，时间很短，留点口水，你忍一下", "timestamp": 1629004378, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "管子很大，你要忍一下～", "timestamp": 1629004413, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我是刚刚发胃病报销的dz\n现在也在做心理建设…感觉问题不大但是很怕有恶性发展", "timestamp": 1629004479, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282314, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "除了胃镜之外 要检查一下幽门螺旋杆菌", "timestamp": 1629004561, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282320, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另外就是胃病 确实要忌口 而且要做好长期养胃的准备 ", "timestamp": 1629004595, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282328, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "小问题，反流性食管炎，这个病是小病，不好治，需要慢慢养", "timestamp": 1629004644, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282369, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般不会第一次就让你做胃镜，感觉你症状跟我比较像，我也是经常胀气偶尔返流，医生说是消化不良，给我开了一些促进胃动力的药，但是这些是治标不治本的，还是得慢慢养，冰的不可以吃，然后平时饭后一定一定要多走动，你可以先试一下饭后散步半小时胀气会不会好一点，如果是的话应该就是消化不良，多坚持运动会好很多，严重的时候吃药", "timestamp": 1629005016, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": 2282314, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave:之前幽门菌在校医院测出来阳性，但说不需要治疗就很迷……", "timestamp": 1629005091, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282387, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": 2282369, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 哎我也是这样的，所以到现在也没做胃镜……", "timestamp": 1629005166, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282531, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz经常不吃早饭，感觉有点问题…", "timestamp": 1629006432, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282534, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "做胃镜疼吗orz", "timestamp": 1629006459, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282653, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以查查幽门螺旋杆菌", "timestamp": 1629007696, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2282738, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 438801, "reply_to": 2282534, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 疼，划拉的嗓子疼一天。以及我就是反流性食管炎，日常反酸，贼难受", "timestamp": 1629008673, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 438801, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "胃经常胀气，有时候有胃酸反流，是什么问题orz，去医院看但害怕胃镜，医生一般怎么检查", "timestamp": 1629004284, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629008676, "url": "", "vote": {}}}